      "source": [
        "# OLD poolparty Tutorial\n",
        "\n",
        "Welcome to the **poolparty** tutorial! This notebook will guide you through using the poolparty package for generating oligonucleotide sequence pools.\n",
        "\n",
        "## What is poolparty?\n",
        "\n",
        "poolparty is a Python package for generating and manipulating oligonucleotide sequences with:\n",
        "- **Lazy Evaluation**: Sequences are computed only when needed\n",
        "- **Flexible Generation**: Choose which pools to iterate completely vs randomly\n",
        "- **Computation Graphs**: Build complex sequence generators through composition\n",
        "- **Multiple Pool Types**: K-mers, selections, shuffled sequences, and more\n",
        "\n",
        "## Installation\n",
        "\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "pip install -e .\n",
        "```\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Table of Contents\n",
        "\n",
        "1. [Basic Pool Operations](#1-Basic-Pool-Operations)\n",
        "   - Concatenation\n",
        "   - Repetition and Slicing\n",
        "\n",
        "2. [KmerPool: Generate K-mers](#2-KmerPool:-Generate-K-mers)\n",
        "   - Creating k-mer pools\n",
        "   - Finite state enumeration\n",
        "\n",
        "3. [ListPool: Choose from a List](#3-ListPool:-Choose-from-a-List)\n",
        "   - Selecting from sequences\n",
        "   - Combinatorial generation\n",
        "   - Reusing pools\n",
        "\n",
        "4. [RandomMutationPool: Random Mutations](#4-RandomMutationPool:-Random-Mutations)\n",
        "   - Uniform mutation rates\n",
        "   - Position-specific mutation rates\n",
        "   - Composition with other pools\n",
        "\n",
        "5. [KMutationPool: Exactly K Mutations](#5-KMutationPool:-Exactly-K-Mutations)\n",
        "   - Non-adjacent mutations\n",
        "   - Adjacent mutations\n",
        "   - Sequential iteration\n",
        "\n",
        "6. [ShuffledPool: Random Shuffles](#6-ShuffledPool:-Random-Shuffles)\n",
        "   - Basic shuffling\n",
        "   - Character composition preservation\n",
        "   - Use case: Random controls\n",
        "\n",
        "7. [SubseqPool: Extract Subsequences](#7-SubseqPool:-Extract-Subsequences)\n",
        "   - Sliding windows\n",
        "   - Non-overlapping tiles\n",
        "   - Offset parameter\n",
        "   - Use case: Motif extraction\n",
        "\n",
        "8. [The generate_seqs() Function](#8-The-generate_seqs()-Function)\n",
        "   - Random generation\n",
        "   - Partial combinatorial completion\n",
        "   - Full combinatorial completion\n",
        "\n",
        "9. [Summary](#9-Summary)\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n"
      ]
